def display_histplot(df, variable, binsize, xlabel, ylabel, title):
    """
        This function for visulize data in bar plot 
    """
    bins = np.arange(0, df[variable].max()+binsize, binsize)
    
    plt.figure(figsize=[10, 8])
    plt.hist(data = df, x = variable, bins = bins)
    plt.xlabel(xlabel)
    plt.ylabel(ylabel)
    plt.title(title)
